== Overview ==
The Vidian Industries' Heavy Shield Displacer is a direct upgrade to the [[Shield Displacer]].

== Where to Acquire ==
The Heavy Shield Displacer can be bought in the workshop or found in caves, vaults, and bot remains in Vulcore.
